            WHEN ((@__currentDate_0 > [p0].[StartDateTime]) AND (@__currentDate_1 < [p0].[EndDateTime])) AND ([p0].[Priority] = 2)

            THEN [p1].[Priority] ELSE 0
        END AS [c], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[StartDateTime], [p1].[EndDateTime], [p1].[Priority]
        FROM [Post] AS [p1]
        INNER JOIN [User] AS [p.User2] ON [p1].[UserId] = [p.User2].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Role] AS [p.User.Role2] ON [p.User2].[RoleId] = [p.User.Role2].[Id]
        WHERE [p1].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ORDER BY [c] DESC, [p1].[CreatedDate] DESC, [p1].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]
) AS [t2] ON [p.PostLikes].[PostId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[c] DESC, [t2].[CreatedDate] DESC, [t2].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p.PostFiles].[Id], [p.PostFiles].[FileId], [p.PostFiles].[IsDeleted], [p.PostFiles].[PostId], [p.File].[Id], [p.File].[ContentType], [p.File].[IsDeleted], [p.File].[Name], [p.File].[SizeKB]
FROM [PostFile] AS [p.PostFiles]
INNER JOIN [File] AS [p.File] ON [p.PostFiles].[FileId] = [p.File].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [p0].[Id], CASE
            WHEN ((@__currentDate_0 > [p0].[StartDateTime]) AND (@__currentDate_1 < [p0].[EndDateTime])) AND ([p0].[Priority] = 2)
            THEN [p0].[Priority] ELSE 0
        END AS [c], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[StartDateTime], [p0].[EndDateTime], [p0].[Priority]
        FROM [Post] AS [p0]
        INNER JOIN [User] AS [p.User0] ON [p0].[UserId] = [p.User0].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Role] AS [p.User.Role0] ON [p.User0].[RoleId] = [p.User.Role0].[Id]
        WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ORDER BY [c] DESC, [p0].[CreatedDate] DESC, [p0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]

            WHEN ((@__currentDate_0 > [p1].[StartDateTime]) AND (@__currentDate_1 < [p1].[EndDateTime])) AND ([p1].[Priority] = 2)

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT TOP(1) [p0].[Id]
        FROM [Post] AS [p0]
        INNER JOIN [User] AS [p.User0] ON [p0].[UserId] = [p.User0].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Role] AS [p.User.Role0] ON [p.User0].[RoleId] = [p.User.Role0].[Id]
        WHERE ([p0].[Id] = @__id_0) AND ([p0].[IsDeleted] = 0)
        ORDER BY [p0].[Id]
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [p.PostFiles].[PostId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
